{
  "stem": "10768.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is their number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is their address.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I cannot drive to them, because there's no post, but if you can.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was writing to Russia, to Irene's mother and three sisters, and they were writing to me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was sending their letter to Irene, and this is how we kept in touch.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Irene found out that her mother and three sisters are alive in Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This, this I thought was of-- of some value-- of some-- to show how the contact of some people, a little thing can help somebody.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because of that, not only because of the sentiment and the friendship from before the war, Irene told to Leo, if you are going to Rita, please take me along.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he in Sanok told her, look, the train-- some trains are running, some are not.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But since I'm a soldier, wherever I will go, you come along with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he somehow managed with a little bit of vodka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, a man has got more tricks of the trade.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came to Rokitnica, to the hospital with Irene.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Irene said to me, listen, I, I survived only because Dr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is an unusual human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Otherwise, there are no Jews in Lesko.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Jewish streets, the Jewish housing is all destroyed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Only the good houses, which were made from brick-- ours was made from brick, but it was very close to the synagogue, so they destroyed it, too.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She told me about my, my parents, that until they took them to Zaslaw, to the ghetto, which they made a regional ghetto-- 25,000 Jews from Sanok, from Wujskie, from Lesko, were in Zaslaw.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- until then, my mother was selling my clothes that I left.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
